ressed":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtagcomponenttokensprovider\/colorcontentpressed","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorContentPressed","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.actionPressed"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider\/colorContentPressed","title":"colorContentPressed","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtagcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of tag input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSInputTag"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllInputTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"InputTagComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tag inputs"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTagComponentTokensProvider"}]}}}